snippet.title: GunGirl 2 Ultimate Trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.gungirl2.com

Download for free at http://www.gungirl2.com/?page_id=31

GunGirl is finally ready for action! She is starring in her second game that can be downloaded for free! In this action platformer, she has to solve quests, get power ups and survive the massive zombie hordes. She is accompanied by her best friend Marvin to stop the apocalypse.

Credits: Game & Trailer by Paul Schneider, music by Josh Whelchel (features: Stephanie Schönhofer (voice), Rachel Denlinger (violin), Rich Brilli (guitar), and Melinda Hershey (voice))
